Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美丽的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:01:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 这种祥和平静的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点冷?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想有人能抱住我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么? 你不是冷吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进屋子喝点可可什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 生什么气呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小卫你这个木头人!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,0){\fn方正粗圆_GBK}{\fs45}{\pos(320,450)}{\b0}{\1c&HD7FFFF&}{\4c&HFFC1C1&}{\shad1}{\bord0}战士的自觉 坚强就在纯真心灵里头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的星空…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"给小淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没见你 我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PS.爸爸也在等你"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 手上拿着什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的信?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 妈妈的信…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 字果然全部都是假名吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈子!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这个时候吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都写了些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫小小兔可以回家了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小小兔怎么说?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是说现在就要马上回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去的话什么时候都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还处在向爸爸妈妈撒娇的年龄啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是想回去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许想回去不肯老实的说出来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔又是不想让别人看到自己软弱的一面类型的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦事又暂时告一段落了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都希望小小兔能回到爸爸妈妈身边去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们就给小小兔留下一个美好的回忆吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么好主意?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢送派对怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 你有时也会说出不错的话来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那赶快去准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就来做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里举办好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫的公寓怎么样? 小兔去问问看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢送派对?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 明天就在小卫的公寓里举办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又还没决定立刻回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家商量后决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情玩吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家这么想我回去?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔这个笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到未来就意味着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见不到小兔小卫与大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和大家在一起  …
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给小小兔准备礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是花掉你所有的积蓄了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是给回到未来的小小兔的礼物!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是金钱所不能衡量的大礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是我小时候特别喜欢的连衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说话我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫 大家都讨厌我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么想?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然为我举办欢送派对…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要让我快点回去似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也希望小小兔能一直留下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 小小兔还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和爸爸妈妈一起生活是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很想见到爸爸妈妈吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子和大家 与小小兔分别也是很伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫也会感到寂寞吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是肯定的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子快睡觉!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白我的心情!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预祝小小兔一帆风顺!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 尽情吃吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 提起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来虽然只比北海道远一点 但是比天国近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候都可以回来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔 你去过天国吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吐槽有什么用?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 让气氛更加热烈吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 小丽来唱首歌!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微波炉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯真心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须收集纯真心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始给小小兔我们的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从真琴开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 这是我做的料理!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在微波炉里叮一下 跟爸爸妈妈一起分享!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是我写的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美真是的 这个时候还谈学习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的学识积累是很重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好学习 累的时候就玩下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个游戏程序 我们也有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的礼物是录有我唱的歌的录音带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的曲子是为小小兔制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的礼物是把大家的相片制作成的一本相册
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们美好的回忆哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 美奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色玫瑰花蕾的花语是纯真与可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与小小兔完全吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能和大家的一起当做礼物吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔…这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然做的不是很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱的小狗背包!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丽! 这不是小狗! 是兔子!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看还真的很像兔子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丽 你总把我当笨蛋看!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们有仇吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 也不用这么说啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说看起来像狗而已!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要一直这么强调狗!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦 不要像狗一样一直汪汪叫好不!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又说了狗了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 手脚笨拙又要逞强!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得满手都是伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴上创可贴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我撕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 把这些放进去 拿来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 这是小兔努力了好久才完成的哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔和小丽想说什么就说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吵架的话也算不错的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要那样的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再送的话我会更伤心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今给大家增添了很多麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了未来的世界 也要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好听爸爸妈妈的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我们向未来的大家问声好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时记得想想我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给她们两人一个独处的空间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间的守护者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天空打开时空之门 向我敞开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等呼唤全能的神的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护者之父克罗诺斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请指引我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请守护我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我打开光明之路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能哭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将回到爸爸妈妈的身边 幸福地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福地过生活了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋小兔 哭的人明明是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪 我明明决定了不哭着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目送你走的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔 我不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要与未来的爸爸妈妈好好相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还存活着死亡幻影的一个卵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个卵变成了戴蒙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城里到处吸取人们的纯真之心!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天王洲 无限学院的废墟!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸! 妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:49.48,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}无差别的夺取人们的纯真心灵 绝不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.31,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}爱与正义的水手服美少女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.23,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 水手队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是 燕尾服假面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:04.91,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}我要代表月亮 惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要纯真心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯真心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:15.56,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}燃烧的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.08,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}曼陀罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.31,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}Sparkling Wide Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微波炉!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:46.94,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}闪耀水幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:58.18,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}维纳斯爱神锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要纯真心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到水晶东京了 …
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯真心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯真心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯真心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有圣杯的话就能变成超级水手月亮了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:19.21,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}{\t(14,\fs23)}{\t(\fry725)}粉红砂糖甜心攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:29.86,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}水手月亮她们是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:33.46,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}你竟然要夺取她们的纯真心灵 绝不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:37.27,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}爱与正义的水手服美少女战士见习生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:39.70,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}水手小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.20,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}我要代表未来的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.15,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是耍帅的时候好不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为人着想的少女心 比任何东西都坚强与美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害美丽少女的事 我燕尾服假面绝不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮 相信友情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 即使没有圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有关怀他人的纯真之心的话 就能保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:40.38,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}月亮螺旋心攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许圣杯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就是关怀他人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美丽的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么又回来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我在大家都很不可靠啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
